{
  "stem": "18670.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father used to tease my mother that she must have a mark on the fence, because all the beggars came.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even during the Depression years, my mother always had bread and had big pot of soup on the-- on the stove to feed them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And now the refugees came, the German refugees.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At least I believed them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, I had something else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know whether I mentioned to you I read a lot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had-- might sound funny too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had books that I read on the toilet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I'm sitting on the toilet, I had books that I read.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I still have that habit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there were two books that I really went through.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One was Hitler's And I believed what he said that he is going to do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the other one was Karl Marx's",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when Hitler came into Austria, I believed that he's going to do it, even though my uncle, his answer was, there are Jews living in Germany, and they are OK.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not a Communist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have never been accused of stealing or doing anything dishonest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why should I worry?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was my mother's brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my-- we had a different thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't expect-- my parents didn't expect anything to happen, except they knew that they had no-- no more livelihood.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They could not exist in a town where they're the only Jews and the street, they could be blocked off easily.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they kept the customers out of the store.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I know what we did is when I came home, I helped shipping back the merchandise.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We knew we were out of business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He couldn't pay his bills.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So for days and days, we packed and shipped it back to the manufacturers in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
